      <title>法官第二次延期冻结特朗普资金计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官在发布第二份阻止该倡议的临时命令时表示，特朗普政府“没有给出任何理由”在不到 24 小时的通知时间内切断可能高达数万亿美元的联邦资金，包括向全国受助人提供的赠款、贷款和其他财政援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢旺达支持的刚果叛军称将开始停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rwanda-backed-m23-rebels-in-congo-say-they-will-begin-a-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国的 M23 叛军表示，他们将于周二开始单方面停火，七国集团要求卢旺达支持的民兵组织停止震动该国东部的攻势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rwanda-backed-m23-rebels-in-congo-say-they-will-begin-a-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可能任命新的 FDIC 和 CFTC 负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-likely-to-make-fresh-picks-to-head-fdic-cftc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，特朗普政府可能会选择新的提名人来监管联邦存款保险公司和商品期货交易委员会，而不是任命这些机构的现任代理负责人来永久领导监管机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-likely-to-make-fresh-picks-to-head-fdic-cftc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:17:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普让市场和企业经历关税过山车式波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-02-03/trump-takes-markets-businesses-on-a-tariff-rollercoaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，一份关于首都金钱、权力和政治的新闻通讯。今天，经济新闻高级作家肖恩·唐南 (Shawn Donnan) 分析了关税波动造成的不确定性。请在此处注册并关注我们 @bpolitics。请在此处向我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-02-03/trump-takes-markets-businesses-on-a-tariff-rollercoaster</guid>
