      <title>巴西挑战马斯克并获胜。现在卢拉正在与欧洲分享经验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-took-on-musk-and-won-now-lula-is-sharing-notes-with-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到伊隆·马斯克政治攻击的欧洲各国政府正在与其他攻击目标交换意见，而这些攻击目标都非常熟悉特斯拉 X 所有者的手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-took-on-musk-and-won-now-lula-is-sharing-notes-with-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
